com.thomsonreuters.ema.access

Interface OmmDateTime

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Data

    public interface OmmDateTime
extends Data
    OmmDateTime represents DateTime info in Omm.
    OmmDateTime encapsulates year, month, day, hour, minute, second, millisecond, microsecond and nanosecond information. OmmDateTime is a read only class.
